类 AbstractKeyedCEPPatternOperator<IN,KEY,OUT,F extends Function>

    public abstract class AbstractKeyedCEPPatternOperator<IN,KEY,OUT,F extends Function>
extends AbstractUdfStreamOperator<OUT,F>
implements OneInputStreamOperator<IN,OUT>, Triggerable<KEY,VoidNamespace>
    Abstract CEP pattern operator for a keyed input stream. For each key, the operator creates a NFA and a priority queue to buffer out of order elements. Both data structures are stored using the managed keyed state. Additionally, the set of all seen keys is kept as part of the operator state. This is necessary to trigger the execution for all keys upon receiving a new watermark.
